data.title: Timepieces: The Best of Eric Clapton - Audio CD By ERIC CLAPTON - VERY GOOD! C1 42280001421
data.meta_description:
This audio CD features the best of Eric Clapton, including tracks produced by Delaney Bramlett, Glyn Johns, and The Dominoes. It was released by Polygram United Kingdom in 1990 and is in the rock genre. The CD grading is very good (VG) and comes in a very good (VG) case and inlay condition.


The album format is CD and it is titled "Timepieces: The Best of Eric Clapton". The release year is 1990 and the edition is the best of. The artist is Eric Clapton, also known as Clapton, Eric. This CD is perfect for music lovers who want to enjoy Eric Clapton's greatest hits.
